cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CE, cs.AI 

The paper involves the use of artificial evolution and artificial neural networks to design and optimize wind turbines, which falls under the category of computational intelligence and robotics. Therefore, cs.NE and cs.RO are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of cooperative coevolution, which falls under the category of control engineering (cs.CE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of artificial neural networks falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
